('d0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000011', 'JOB', 'SAP Consultants (SD / MM / PP / QM)', 'SAP Consultants (SD / MM / PP / QM) at Pertemps ERP.', ARRAY['SAP/ERP Consulting','Development'], '{"external_id": "public-job-00025", "requirements_text": "Tasks Working with a global organisation scaling its SAP S/4HANA landscape, I\u2019m looking to connect with SAP Consultants across multiple modules: \ud83d\udd39 SD (Sales &#x26; Distribution) \ud83d\udd39 MM / QM (Materials Management / Quality Management) \ud83d\udd39 MM / PP (Materials Management / Production Planning) Requirements 3+ years of SAP customising experience (SD, MM, PP, or QM) Strong understanding of business processes &#x26; stakeholder collaboration S/4HANA exposure is a plus English required (German beneficial, not essential) Benefits \u2714\ufe0f Attractive salary &#x26; benefits \u2714\ufe0f Hybrid working (central Hamburg location) \u2714\ufe0f Relocation support available \u2714\ufe0f Modern S/4HANA landscape \u2714\ufe0f International projects &#x26; long-term development opportunities This is a great opportunity to join a company where you can influence global processes and be part of a highly collaborative SAP environment. Interested or curious to learn more? Feel free to message me directly or comment below. #SAP #S4HANA #SAPJobs #SAPConsultant #HamburgJobs #TechCareers Find more English Speaking Jobs in Germany on Arbeitnow", "skills_required": ["SAP/ERP Consulting", "Development"], "work_mode": "HYBRID", "employment_type": "FREELANCE", "external_url": "https://www.arbeitnow.com/jobs/companies/pertemps-erp/sap-consultants-sd-mm-pp-qm-hamburg-321805"}'::jsonb, 'DE', true, '[-2.28401661,-0.50690353,2.57710767,0.32141516,-2.52881908,-3.51063752,0.98417431,0.09534007,1.21524954,0.57034332,-0.85132980,-1.81783128,-2.52387452,1.04409635,-1.12059879,-0.14820722,-1.17320764,2.19453430,-0.39500165,1.46754885,-1.87318933,-4.80649090,0.71328604,-2.35638499,-2.66716218,-0.45610100,-0.86688077,-2.28182435,-0.7